{"tid":1457671,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡思貝發流淚照片   許廷鏗發聲即被指責","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:12:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb09709be6a1d892d19fecb617fb775079013a0","tid":1457671,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3150962/org/e0a8ef628e6ea125317c043f816c7fac.png/opPJKAP3FKk7QPfLF-pUj1b_fe9Yv-pWFd3gCxXd4As?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3150962%2Forg%2Fe0a8ef628e6ea125317c043f816c7fac.png%2FopPJKAP3FKk7QPfLF-pUj1b_fe9Yv-pWFd3gCxXd4As%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=9b40183e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日（11日）本港多區出現反修例示威，防暴警到場驅趕，期間一度於港鐵葵芳站、太古站內發射催淚彈，亦有市民被制服在地上後仍被警員亂棍狂毆，亦有少女被警察被布袋彈射擊，導致右眼球爆裂，事件激發民憤。有網民發起「警察還眼」行動，呼籲市民於今午（12日)到香港機場聚集，為傷者討回公道。蔡思貝於IG STORY上載眼晴流淚嘅照片，未有加上任何文字，只係得一個非常微細嘅天平emoji，未知是否為受傷少女討回公道。反觀之前曾在「反修例」初期發聲嘅唐詩詠、林秀怡、馮盈盈等人，其社交網站則暫時未有任何更新。<br />\n<br />\n而許廷鏗今午在其社交網發文表示「小時候認知「正確」的定義 ，由細到大的價值觀，一直以來看到「人性」的定位 好像一下子全都推翻了。最近發生好多好多事，會很沮喪，會很無奈。越有能力的就應該越懂得解決與處理問題，掌握權力的就更加要懂得負責與承擔事情。」即獲不少網民讚好，但亦有部份的簡體字留言，指他「港獨」。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/362943/蔡思貝發流淚照片有寓意-許廷鏗發聲即被指責</code></pre>"},{"pid":"b7ec2c491a7c25fe3997dccbfaa8caa9d3f7157c","tid":1457671,"uid":217762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"821"},{"pid":"27165848fb5f24898a2e468a8d8ba6c5adfe12e0","tid":1457671,"uid":298077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:05:00.000Z","msg":"唔發聲/發聲都死"},{"pid":"1d8f59c434d7b9e93e207bdd64ba30f670ccf2ef","tid":1457671,"uid":76632,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:05:25.000Z","msg":"兩個達哥都開始發聲"},{"pid":"aef0102240c4ab6ed7afc76c7ad0229d082c8b60","tid":1457671,"uid":72037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:12:20.000Z","msg":"支那狗cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4382598b0747eb7d9152bb4d5c7016bd91a7efcd","tid":1457671,"uid":8439,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:13:14.000Z","msg":"支那狗除左港獨仲識咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd924517ba2075bde94437c45278aad130d66f4a","tid":1457671,"uid":835,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:13:44.000Z","msg":"好似比比鳥徐天佑咁,肯表態既大家應該實際支持佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e5c4c7e3a650c984ca89c526cfcf7ad64c50dd","tid":1457671,"uid":65380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:14:38.000Z","msg":"牙醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b04f711f0e325dbb36172c9cba64b34ee9a824c","tid":1457671,"uid":123989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:15:50.000Z","msg":"思達<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131875ac8675ac611d79b045bc8440775696e022","tid":1457671,"uid":213819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:22:04.000Z","msg":"咩都港獨 聽到悶"},{"pid":"86b223260c7c184d87059f8c4bba2a86768f799e","tid":1457671,"uid":297139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:12:04.000Z","msg":"蔡思貝老豆唔係差佬黎咩"}]}